# Always Use Full URLs

When providing links or page references to the user, always include the full URL with domain.

## Rules

- Always prefix paths with `https://www.chatfpl.ai`
- Never give bare slugs like `/fpl/injuries` or `devcaptains`
- Always give clickable full URLs like `https://www.chatfpl.ai/fpl/injuries`

## Examples

❌ BAD
```
/fpl/injuries
devcaptains
/fpl/compare/haaland/salah
```

✅ GOOD
```
https://www.chatfpl.ai/fpl/injuries
https://www.chatfpl.ai/devcaptains
https://www.chatfpl.ai/fpl/compare/haaland/salah
```
